ter was born and named Mary in her sister's memory. The second Mary later married Julius Yemans Dewey and was the mother of Admiral George Dewey, hero of Manila Bay 1898."}],"slug":"mary-perrin-1758"}},"burialCemetery":null,"institutionsById":{},"crossConnections":[]}